qMeasure.qDef:
Pick(Balance_calculation,   
    //Default calcuation
     Num(Sum(AmountLC),ONLY(Balance_RowNumFormatCode)),
    //Format code has to be set on each row to be able to handle blank rows
     ' ',
    //Cellvalue in Excel = 3 (Calcuation = 3 in application) Margin calculation with 1 calculation input 
     Num(Sum(AmountLC)/Sum(IF(Balance_rowNumber<=Balance_CalculationInput1,AmountLC,0)),ONLY(Balance_RowNumFormatCode))
	//This is the generic solution for minimum maintenance and expression complexity. 
	//For maximum performance in some cases it may be more efficient to use multiple specific expressions with SET-analysis rather than the if-statement below
     )
